Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.01,0:41:27.05,字幕,,0,0,0,,在海水中驰骋\N{\fs90}In the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.65,0:41:34.57,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为玛莎拉蒂的抗锈做的极好\N{\fs90}You can take a Maserati in the sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.69,0:41:38.89,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以你能将它带入海中\N{\fs90}because the rust-proofing is so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.96,0:41:42.37,字幕,,0,0,0,,之后 我们一边散步欣赏风景\N{\fs90}After that, we enjoyed a picturesque walk
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.42,0:41:44.45,字幕,,0,0,0,,一边进行哲学辩论\N{\fs90}and a philosophical debate.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.48,0:41:47.68,字幕,,0,0,0,,有比其他男人给你背上抹防晒\N{\fs90}Is there anything on earth which is worse
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.77,0:41:50.07,字幕,,0,0,0,,更糟的事吗\N{\fs90}than having another man put sun cream on your back?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.14,0:41:52.08,字幕,,0,0,0,,我从未体验过\N{\fs90}I've never experienced that.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.17,0:41:54.44,字幕,,0,0,0,,然后我们运动了一番\N{\fs90}And then we played some sport.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.57,0:41:56.18,字幕,,0,0,0,,在法国南部的沙滩上\N{\fs90}Penalty shoot-out
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.24,0:41:59.45,字幕,,0,0,0,,开玛莎拉蒂进行点球大战\N{\fs90}in Maseratis on a beach in northern France.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.82,0:42:11.26,字幕,,0,0,0,,球炸了后\N{\fs90}With our ball gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.32,0:42:13.42,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们回到了诺曼底之旅\N{\fs90}we continued on our tour of Normandy,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.57,0:42:18.23,字幕,,0,0,0,,而体弱多病的同事却一直在呻吟\N{\fs90}with our badly-built colleague moaning constantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.30,0:42:22.71,字幕,,0,0,0,,谁把船长换成了一个老太太\N{\fs90}Has he been swapped for an old lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.80,0:42:24.77,字幕,,0,0,0,,他一直是个老太太\N{\fs90}He's always been an old lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.88,0:42:26.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,他生下来就是个老太太\N{\fs90}He was born an old lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.81,0:42:29.62,字幕,,0,0,0,,恭喜你 梅夫人 您生了个老太太\N{\fs90}"Congratulations, Mrs May. It's an old lady!"
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.44,0:42:37.02,字幕,,0,0,0,,夜色降临时 我们到达了翁弗勒尔古镇\N{\fs90}As darkness fell, we reached the ancient town of Honfleur,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.08,0:42:39.05,字幕,,0,0,0,,决定在此留宿一夜\N{\fs90}where we decided to spend the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.12,0:42:41.75,字幕,,0,0,0,,但 为了抵达酒店\N{\fs90}Unfortunately, to reach our hotel,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.82,0:42:43.89,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们得在迷宫般的\N{\fs90}we had to navigate through a maze
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.96,0:42:46.63,字幕,,0,0,0,,中世纪狭窄街道中行驶\N{\fs90}of tiny, medieval streets.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.83,0:42:52.46,字幕,,0,0,0,,不好意思 抱歉\N{\fs90}Pardon. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.53,0:42:55.64,字幕,,0,0,0,,这太窄了 不是吗\N{\fs90}This is narrow. Isn't it narrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.30,0:42:59.91,字幕,,0,0,0,,别啊\N{\fs90}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.64,0:43:07.31,字幕,,0,0,0,,以前没有动力转向的时候\N{\fs90}How did people manage in this town in the olden days
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.42,0:43:09.65,字幕,,0,0,0,,这里的人都怎么开车的\N{\fs90}when nobody had power steering?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.68,0:43:11.92,字幕,,0,0,0,,哦不\N{\fs90}Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.45,0:43:15.66,字幕,,0,0,0,,这该怎么办\N{\fs90}I do that how?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.89,0:43:21.09,字幕,,0,0,0,,哦我的天哪\N{\fs90}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.29,0:43:24.25,字幕,,0,0,0,,我彻底卡住了\N{\fs90}I'm totally stuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.73,0:43:30.20,字幕,,0,0,0,,都是石子路\N{\fs90}Ow, ow, ow, ow. Cobbles.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.84,0:43:36.98,字幕,,0,0,0,,我的神啊\N{\fs90}God almighty.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.71,0:43:40.75,字幕,,0,0,0,,我不确定这可行\N{\fs90}I'm not sure that's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.25,0:43:51.59,字幕,,0,0,0,,卧了个…那是\N{\fs90}Oh, for... Is that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.69,0:43:53.39,字幕,,0,0,0,,你挡道了\N{\fs90}You're in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.46,0:43:55.70,字幕,,0,0,0,,我这边是单行道\N{\fs90}It's a one-way street my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.76,0:43:57.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,它的确是单行道\N{\fs90}It's a one-way street, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.06,0:43:59.23,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以我和别的车\N{\fs90}That's why me and the other cars
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.30,0:44:01.10,字幕,,0,0,0,,都在往这方向开\N{\fs90}are all coming this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.17,0:44:04.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,别让我用这破转向再退回去\N{\fs90}Please don't make me back up with this steering.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.47,0:44:07.44,字幕,,0,0,0,,来吧 就当锻炼了\N{\fs90}Come on, it's a workout.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.51,0:44:09.24,字幕,,0,0,0,,哈蒙德 我要杀了你\N{\fs90}Hammond, I am gonna kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.31,0:44:11.84,字幕,,0,0,0,,请稍等\N{\fs90}Moment, s'il vous plaît.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.45,0:44:15.45,字幕,,0,0,0,,我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.51,0:44:19.48,字幕,,0,0,0,,他开车子
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.55,0:44:20.85,字幕,,0,0,0,,像大猩猩一样
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.49,0:44:27.22,字幕,,0,0,0,,你要的火腿\N{\fs90}Vous devrez...le jambon
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.32,0:44:28.64,副本字幕,,0,0,0,,要开走 这里堵了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.19,0:44:30.92,副本字幕,,0,0,0,,前面左转
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.92,0:44:33.09,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们就搞定啦
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.64,0:44:33.20,副本字幕,,0,0,0,,我们就是蘑菇了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.40,0:44:38.24,字幕,,0,0,0,,等杰里米移开了 我也可以继续了\N{\fs90}With Jeremy out of the way, I could move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.30,0:44:40.14,字幕,,0,0,0,,但是接着\N{\fs90}But then...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.21,0:44:43.54,字幕,,0,0,0,,哈蒙德 那个开黄灯过来的是你吗\N{\fs90}Hammond, is that you with yellow lights coming up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.85,0:44:46.60,字幕,,0,0,0,,-我的天 -这真不走运\N{\fs90}- Oh, my God. - That's a bit of bad luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.71,0:44:48.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,你得倒车了 对吧\N{\fs90}You're going to have to reverse up there, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.82,0:44:51.82,字幕,,0,0,0,,我不能 因为这里窄得离谱\N{\fs90}I can't back up because it's preposterously narrow
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.91,0:44:54.29,字幕,,0,0,0,,而且我没法转头看后面\N{\fs90}and I can't swivel my head round to look behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.35,0:44:55.60,字幕,,0,0,0,,你说该咋办\N{\fs90}So now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.74,0:44:57.51,字幕,,0,0,0,,好吧 我在这单行道上\N{\fs90}Well, I'm going the right way
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.54,0:44:58.71,字幕,,0,0,0,,开的是正确的方向\N{\fs90}down the one-way street,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.77,0:45:00.09,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以路权归我\N{\fs90}so I have right of way.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.86,0:45:04.86,字幕,,0,0,0,,不好意思哈蒙德 你要帮我指挥一下\N{\fs90}Sorry, Hammond, you'll have to direct me a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.93,0:45:08.07,字幕,,0,0,0,,-右一点 -我的右还是你的右\N{\fs90}- Right a bit. - My right or your right?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.13,0:45:10.48,字幕,,0,0,0,,好吧 我的右 也就是你的左\N{\fs90}Well, my right. Which is your left
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.57,0:45:12.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,但是你在倒车\N{\fs90}but you're steering in reverse.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.07,0:45:13.77,字幕,,0,0,0,,停在那里 我要往左了\N{\fs90}Hold it there and I'll go left.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.81,0:45:15.17,字幕,,0,0,0,,你的左还是我的左\N{\fs90}Your left or my left?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.24,0:45:17.31,字幕,,0,0,0,,我看的是你的右边 我的左边\N{\fs90}Your right, my left as I'm looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.38,0:45:20.20,字幕,,0,0,0,,而你所看的你的右边 也就是你的右边\N{\fs90}And your right as you're looking, i.e. your right.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.81,0:45:23.55,字幕,,0,0,0,,我找到宾馆了\N{\fs90}I had found the hotel,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.62,0:45:26.71,字幕,,0,0,0,,但是显然我的同事们还要一会\N{\fs90}but clearly my colleagues were going to be a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.77,0:45:28.97,字幕,,0,0,0,,当你说我的左边 你是指我的左边吗\N{\fs90}When you say my left, do you mean my left
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.02,0:45:30.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,是我要去的这个方向\N{\fs90}if I'm facing the way I'm going
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.48,0:45:31.99,字幕,,0,0,0,,还是我面朝的方向\N{\fs90}or facing the way I'm facing?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.06,0:45:33.25,字幕,,0,0,0,,问的好\N{\fs90}Good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.37,0:45:36.66,字幕,,0,0,0,,你的左边还是我的右边\N{\fs90}Your left is still my right.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.80,0:45:40.53,字幕,,0,0,0,,但是你在倒车 就这么开\N{\fs90}But you're going backwards. Just drive backwards!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.60,0:45:43.14,字幕,,0,0,0,,我要去宾馆了但是我要把这个开着\N{\fs90}I'm going to the hotel now but I'll leave this on
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.22,0:45:45.64,字幕,,0,0,0,,你能实时监听他们的动向\N{\fs90}so you can stay in tune with what they're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.70,0:45:48.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,我才不相信我开错路\N{\fs90}I don't believe I've come the wrong way
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.17,0:45:49.84,字幕,,0,0,0,,到了一条单行道上 我知道的\N{\fs90}down a one-way street. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.91,0:45:52.81,字幕,,0,0,0,,你在让处境变好还是变差\N{\fs90}Are you making your situation better or worse?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.88,0:45:56.51,字幕,,0,0,0,,更好 更差 更好 更差\N{\fs90}Better? Worse? Better? Worse?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.68,0:46:00.22,字幕,,0,0,0,,当理查德和船长终于和我一起\N{\fs90}When Richard and James did finally join me,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.28,0:46:01.65,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们在晚餐时反思了一下\N{\fs90}we reflected over dinner
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.71,0:46:04.28,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们在法国北部的这些时间\N{\fs90}about our time in the north of France.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.29,0:46:07.28,字幕,,0,0,0,,这是段极好的旅程\N{\fs90}It's been just a tremendous journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.40,0:46:09.69,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们外面有三辆玛莎拉蒂 开了三天\N{\fs90}We've had three Maseratis out here for three days
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.83,0:46:12.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,却不能开个过瘾\N{\fs90}and we've only had one minor fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.46,0:46:15.63,字幕,,0,0,0,,我能说 而且很认真的说\N{\fs90}Can I just say, and I'm being absolutely honest here,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.70,0:46:17.07,字幕,,0,0,0,,我爱我的玛莎拉蒂\N{\fs90}I love my Maserati.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.14,0:46:19.54,字幕,,0,0,0,,-我彻底迷上了它 -是的\N{\fs90}- I've totally fallen for it. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.60,0:46:21.64,字幕,,0,0,0,,我很喜欢我的车\N{\fs90}I really like mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.71,0:46:23.14,字幕,,0,0,0,,没有车的声浪更动听\N{\fs90}No car makes a better noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.21,0:46:25.24,字幕,,0,0,0,,这是最动听的2.0升发动机\N{\fs90}No two-litre car makes a better noise than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.31,0:46:27.31,字幕,,0,0,0,,我比启程的时候更爱它\N{\fs90}I love it more now than when I started.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.38,0:46:28.85,字幕,,0,0,0,,我绝对想把它留下\N{\fs90}I definitely want to keep mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.91,0:46:32.05,字幕,,0,0,0,,我想知道用两只手开会是什么感觉\N{\fs90}I want to know what it's like to drive with two arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.12,0:46:34.15,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为我们都太喜欢这些车了\N{\fs90}Because we all loved our cars so much,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.22,0:46:36.66,字幕,,0,0,0,,我觉得应该用一个火辣的高潮\N{\fs90}I decided we should end our road trip
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.72,0:46:39.06,字幕,,0,0,0,,来结束这次旅行\N{\fs90}with a spicy climax.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.12,0:46:42.29,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们为什么不比赛谁先开回英国\N{\fs90}Why don't we race back to England, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.36,0:46:45.30,字幕,,0,0,0,,一大早出发 最后一个回到那里的\N{\fs90}First thing in the morning. Last one back there...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.43,0:46:48.13,字幕,,0,0,0,,要把车卖了\N{\fs90}has to sell their car.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.20,0:46:50.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,-噢 这好残忍  -太残酷了\N{\fs90}- Ooh, that's cruel. - That's harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.40,0:46:54.14,字幕,,0,0,0,,这对我不太公平吧 不是吗\N{\fs90}It's not entirely fair on me, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.27,0:46:56.68,字幕,,0,0,0,,为什么不\N{\fs90}Hello. Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.77,0:46:58.88,字幕,,0,0,0,,你自己决定只带一只胳膊来\N{\fs90}You chose to come equipped with one arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.88,0:47:00.85,字幕,,0,0,0,,这是你的问题 不是我们的\N{\fs90}It's your issue, not ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.94,0:47:03.38,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以我们从这里同时出发\N{\fs90}So we set off from here, all at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.45,0:47:07.25,字幕,,0,0,0,,任何路线 最后一个\N{\fs90}Any route you like. Last one...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.89,0:47:09.92,字幕,,0,0,0,,回到英国本土的\N{\fs90}back on English soil,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.99,0:47:11.51,字幕,,0,0,0,,要把车卖了\N{\fs90}has to sell their car.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.60,0:47:13.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,我资瓷 来赌一把\N{\fs90}I'm up for it. I'll risk it
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.45,0:47:15.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为那会让回家的路程变得很刺激\N{\fs90}cos that'll make the trip home exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.40,0:47:17.03,字幕,,0,0,0,,我会做的 最后一个到家\N{\fs90}I'll do it. Last one home...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.07,0:47:25.91,字幕,,0,0,0,,破晓时分\N{\fs90}As dawn broke,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.94,0:47:27.91,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们在宾馆外一字排开\N{\fs90}we lined up outside the hotel,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.97,0:47:29.91,字幕,,0,0,0,,准备出发\N{\fs90}ready for the off.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.98,0:47:32.20,字幕,,0,0,0,,先生们 现在时早上9:56分\N{\fs90}Gentlemen, it's ten to four in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.31,0:47:33.57,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们走吧\N{\fs90}Let's do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.65,0:47:36.32,字幕,,0,0,0,,三 二 一 开始\N{\fs90}In three, two, one... Begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.22,0:47:47.03,字幕,,0,0,0,,冲啊\N{\fs90}Blast!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.09,0:47:48.53,字幕,,0,0,0,,走\N{\fs90}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.20,0:47:54.30,字幕,,0,0,0,,不 不\N{\fs90}No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.37,0:47:56.54,字幕,,0,0,0,,不惜任何代价 我要赢\N{\fs90}At all costs, I am winning this.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.54,0:48:05.54,字幕,,0,0,0,,这是辆典型的意大利车\N{\fs90}This is typical. Typical of Italian cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.62,0:48:07.95,字幕,,0,0,0,,它等到你最需要它的时候\N{\fs90}They wait until you really need them,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.01,0:48:10.95,字幕,,0,0,0,,然后才出差错\N{\fs90}and then they go wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.98,0:48:12.95,字幕,,0,0,0,,"哦亲爱的 我快生啦 你快点"\N{\fs90}“Oh, darling, darling, I'm in labour! Quickly!"
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.02,0:48:15.22,字幕,,0,0,0,,我开着玛莎拉蒂在路上呢\N{\fs90}"Yes, I'm on my way in my Maserati."
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.09,0:48:21.57,字幕,,0,0,0,,好的 走这边\N{\fs90}Right. Up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.49,0:48:25.45,字幕,,0,0,0,,这里很熟悉 不是好兆头\N{\fs90}Some of this is familiar, which is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.60,0:48:29.63,字幕,,0,0,0,,哦不 现在别迷路啊\N{\fs90}Oh, no, not lost now.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.74,0:48:32.80,字幕,,0,0,0,,我又一次哄开心我的车\N{\fs90}Once again, I'd managed to coax my car
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.91,0:48:34.07,字幕,,0,0,0,,让它正常工作\N{\fs90}into some kind of life
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.14,0:48:35.87,字幕,,0,0,0,,我出发了\N{\fs90}and I was on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.98,0:48:38.14,字幕,,0,0,0,,驶出镇子\N{\fs90}So, straight out of town.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.98,0:48:44.22,字幕,,0,0,0,,听着还行\N{\fs90}Sounding healthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.28,0:48:46.52,字幕,,0,0,0,,在最高20km/h的时速下\N{\fs90}With a top speed of about 12,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.59,0:48:49.12,字幕,,0,0,0,,前往勒阿弗尔的渡船码头\N{\fs90}I was headed for the ferry port of Le Havre.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.19,0:48:50.95,字幕,,0,0,0,,问题是 按理说\N{\fs90}The trouble is that logically,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.95,0:48:53.63,字幕,,0,0,0,,他们两人也会如此\N{\fs90}the others would be doing the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.03,0:49:00.37,字幕,,0,0,0,,车啊 清清你的嗓子 求你了\N{\fs90}Car, clear your throat, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.67,0:49:04.60,字幕,,0,0,0,,我出来了\N{\fs90}I'm out!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.67,0:49:06.47,字幕,,0,0,0,,好的 英国我来了\N{\fs90}Right, England, here I come.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.27,0:49:12.01,字幕,,0,0,0,,求你了 清清嗓子吧\N{\fs90}Clear your throat, car! Clear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.08,0:49:13.75,字幕,,0,0,0,,不然我们就要垫底了\N{\fs90}Or we shall be last.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.81,0:49:16.94,字幕,,0,0,0,,我就得把你卖了 而且我绝对不会卖给好人\N{\fs90}And then I shall have to sell you, and I won't sell you to someone nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.62,0:49:20.62,字幕,,0,0,0,,你知道有人会艹车\N{\fs90}You know that man who has sex with his cars
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.69,0:49:23.12,字幕,,0,0,0,,还会把照片发到网上\N{\fs90}and then puts pictures of it on the internet?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.19,0:49:24.92,字幕,,0,0,0,,我要把你卖给他\N{\fs90}I'm going to sell you to him
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.02,0:49:28.39,字幕,,0,0,0,,除非你走起来 现在 走啊\N{\fs90}unless you get going. Now, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.46,0:49:31.10,字幕,,0,0,0,,-等等 -不\N{\fs90}- Hang on a minute. - No!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.16,0:49:33.13,字幕,,0,0,0,,不不不\N{\fs90}No, no, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.07,0:49:39.30,字幕,,0,0,0,,路况真棒\N{\fs90}Big road. Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.04,0:49:43.38,字幕,,0,0,0,,与此同时\N{\fs90}James, meanwhile,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.44,0:49:45.65,字幕,,0,0,0,,船长还在后面闲逛\N{\fs90}was dawdling along at the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.71,0:49:49.81,字幕,,0,0,0,,他似乎毫不在乎这事\N{\fs90}Yet he seemed strangely unconcerned about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.88,0:49:52.75,字幕,,0,0,0,,从表面上看 这不太算是一场比赛\N{\fs90}On the face of it, viewers, this isn't much of a race,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.82,0:49:55.48,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为我的车是最慢的 我们已经知道了\N{\fs90}because I've got the slowest car, we already know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.57,0:49:57.62,字幕,,0,0,0,,我只能用一只胳膊\N{\fs90}I only have the use of one arm
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.71,0:49:59.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,而且我还得握着\N{\fs90}and I'm steering
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.40,0:50:02.09,字幕,,0,0,0,,方向盘上的尖叫蛙来转向\N{\fs90}with a squeaky frog bolted to the wheel.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.16,0:50:04.76,字幕,,0,0,0,,然而 并没有那么简单\N{\fs90}However, it's not that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.83,0:50:07.80,字幕,,0,0,0,,事实上\N{\fs90}In fact,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.87,0:50:10.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,我相信我会是第一\N{\fs90}I believe I will be first.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.07,0:50:13.17,字幕,,0,0,0,,在后的将要在前\N{\fs90}Because he who is last shall be first.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.24,0:50:15.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,圣经记载说\N{\fs90}As we know.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.81,0:50:20.85,字幕,,0,0,0,,现在上高速公路\N{\fs90}Coming up now to the motorway.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.82,0:50:26.75,字幕,,0,0,0,,加油啊 拜托\N{\fs90}Come on, car. Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.49,0:50:32.52,字幕,,0,0,0,,我已经成功开上匝道了\N{\fs90}It's made it up the slip road.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.59,0:50:35.63,字幕,,0,0,0,,你可曾见过比这辆\N{\fs90}Have you ever known a car with more spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.69,0:50:38.62,字幕,,0,0,0,,华丽的玛莎拉蒂更有个性的车\N{\fs90}than this magnificent Maserati?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.71,0:50:42.42,字幕,,0,0,0,,然而 匝道的坡度比起前方的挑战\N{\fs90}However, the gradient on the slip road was nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.54,0:50:44.60,字幕,,0,0,0,,根本算不上什么\N{\fs90}compared to what lay ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.60,0:50:49.67,注释,,0,0,0,,此为诺曼底大桥
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.67,0:50:51.28,字幕,,0,0,0,,哦 我的姑奶奶啊\N{\fs90}Oh, my giddy aunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.98,0:50:57.28,字幕,,0,0,0,,港口在哪里\N{\fs90}Port, where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.35,0:50:59.94,字幕,,0,0,0,,如果我第一个到那里 我得等渡轮\N{\fs90}If I get there first, I've got to wait for the ferry.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.97,0:51:02.22,字幕,,0,0,0,,他们就会赶上我 但是我在队伍前面\N{\fs90}They could catch up, but I'll be ahead in the queue.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.34,0:51:05.25,字幕,,0,0,0,,第一个上船的人也第一个下船\N{\fs90}Whoever gets on the boat first gets off the boat first,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.34,0:51:06.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,这是一定的\N{\fs90}and you can't change that.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.82,0:51:09.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,如果他们先上船\N{\fs90}First on the boat is first off the boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.40,0:51:10.25,字幕,,0,0,0,,他们就赢了\N{\fs90}They win.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.97,0:51:21.94,字幕,,0,0,0,,好的 冷静点 杰里米\N{\fs90}Right, calm, Jeremy, calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.97,0:51:23.38,字幕,,0,0,0,,你在高速公路上\N{\fs90}You're on a motorway.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.44,0:51:25.21,字幕,,0,0,0,,在一座大桥上\N{\fs90}On an enormous bridge,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.28,0:51:27.15,字幕,,0,0,0,,被很多重卡包围\N{\fs90}surrounded by many heavy lorries.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.42,0:51:32.38,字幕,,0,0,0,,哦不\N{\fs90}Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.45,0:51:34.82,字幕,,0,0,0,,我可以听到排气在噼啪响\N{\fs90}I can hear the exhaust spluttering.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.89,0:51:38.36,字幕,,0,0,0,,烟 冒出了好多烟\N{\fs90}Smoke. A lot of smoke now.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.96,0:51:44.16,字幕,,0,0,0,,拜托 振作点\N{\fs90}Please! Please work!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.73,0:51:49.17,字幕,,0,0,0,,万幸 我到了桥顶\N{\fs90}Mercifully, I reach the top of the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.17,0:51:51.70,字幕,,0,0,0,,但是\N{\fs90}But then...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.07,0:51:56.38,字幕,,0,0,0,,它挂了\N{\fs90}It's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.44,0:51:59.31,字幕,,0,0,0,,卧槽 刹车失灵了\N{\fs90}Shit, I've lost braking. I have lost braking.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.38,0:52:02.38,字幕,,0,0,0,,真他妈的 手刹也不行了\N{\fs90}Bloody hell. Handbrake not working, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.45,0:52:04.92,字幕,,0,0,0,,我的刹车完全失灵了\N{\fs90}I've lost all brakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.98,0:52:07.22,字幕,,0,0,0,,我现在别无选择\N{\fs90}There was only one thing for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.89,0:52:13.43,字幕,,0,0,0,,我没有刹车\N{\fs90}I have no brakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.49,0:52:14.93,字幕,,0,0,0,,你刚撞了我们的车\N{\fs90}You've just hit our car!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.99,0:52:16.48,字幕,,0,0,0,,我刹车坏了\N{\fs90}I haven't got any brakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.88,0:52:18.05,字幕,,0,0,0,,被当成刹车来用\N{\fs90}They're not pleased
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.14,0:52:20.63,字幕,,0,0,0,,他们似乎不太高兴\N{\fs90}about being used as a brake.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.70,0:52:22.20,字幕,,0,0,0,,顺便一提 在法国公路上\N{\fs90}This is totally illegal, by the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.34,0:52:23.65,字幕,,0,0,0,,这是完全违法的\N{\fs90}on a French motorway.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.77,0:52:25.51,字幕,,0,0,0,,好的 我没有刹车\N{\fs90}Right, so I've no brakes
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.57,0:52:26.71,字幕,,0,0,0,,没有动力\N{\fs90}and no engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.31,0:52:34.45,字幕,,0,0,0,,杰里米 好好想想\N{\fs90}Think, Jeremy, think.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.02,0:52:39.65,字幕,,0,0,0,,港口 你好\N{\fs90}Port. Yes, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.72,0:52:42.12,字幕,,0,0,0,,对杰里米的状况毫不知情\N{\fs90}Unaware of Jeremy's problems,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.22,0:52:44.52,字幕,,0,0,0,,我继续前行\N{\fs90}I was keeping the hammer down.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.33,0:52:47.79,字幕,,0,0,0,,度假者\N{\fs90}Holiday-makers!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.86,0:52:50.66,字幕,,0,0,0,,我恨度假者\N{\fs90}I hate holiday-makers!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.10,0:52:55.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,卡车\N{\fs90}Trucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.47,0:52:58.60,字幕,,0,0,0,,我要超过所有的卡车\N{\fs90}I'm going to get caught up with all the trucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.67,0:53:01.84,字幕,,0,0,0,,与此同时 回到船长那边\N{\fs90}Meanwhile, back in the land of Captain Cryptic...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.61,0:53:09.25,字幕,,0,0,0,,你知道吗 我很享受这个过程\N{\fs90}Do you know, I'm so relaxed about this,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.31,0:53:10.60,字幕,,0,0,0,,我想 再过一会\N{\fs90}I think, in a short while,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.65,0:53:12.88,字幕,,0,0,0,,我可能会停下来喝一杯咖啡\N{\fs90}I might stop for a pleasant coffee
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.95,0:53:15.52,字幕,,0,0,0,,读读报纸\N{\fs90}and a read of the newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.29,0:53:20.33,字幕,,0,0,0,,我在赶时间 抱歉了伙计\N{\fs90}Not got time for you, mate. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.39,0:53:22.49,字幕,,0,0,0,,有车\N{\fs90}Car! Car!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.00,0:53:27.80,字幕,,0,0,0,,天啊 又一个环岛\N{\fs90}Oh, God. Another roundabout.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.91,0:53:29.37,字幕,,0,0,0,,好像我在市中心一样\N{\fs90}It's like I'm in the middle of bloody town.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.64,0:53:33.67,字幕,,0,0,0,,我得自己找条路\N{\fs90}I need to find my own route.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.74,0:53:35.84,字幕,,0,0,0,,这里肯定有小路能穿出去\N{\fs90}There must be sneaky ways through.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.61,0:53:44.32,字幕,,0,0,0,,会好的 会好的\N{\fs90}This could be good. This could be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.06,0:53:54.66,字幕,,0,0,0,,走这边\N{\fs90}Down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.73,0:53:56.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,噢\N{\fs90}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.73,0:53:58.60,字幕,,0,0,0,,死胡同\N{\fs90}Dead end.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.66,0:54:00.87,字幕,,0,0,0,,不是这边 见鬼了\N{\fs90}Not that way. Bloody hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.02,0:54:20.82,字幕,,0,0,0,,我抄近路的计划并没奏效\N{\fs90}My shortcut wasn't going well.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.92,0:54:27.73,字幕,,0,0,0,,他们在哪儿 更重要的我在哪儿\N{\fs90}Where are they and more importantly where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.86,0:54:35.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,这招走错了 我搞砸了\N{\fs90}This was a mistake. This is making things worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.07,0:54:37.07,字幕,,0,0,0,,这只是浪费时间\N{\fs90}It's just costing time.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.14,0:54:39.04,字幕,,0,0,0,,事实证明\N{\fs90}And, as it turned out,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.10,0:54:42.24,字幕,,0,0,0,,我现在最大的敌人就是时间\N{\fs90}time was something I didn't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.34,0:54:44.98,字幕,,0,0,0,,我现在只剩一个涡轮了\N{\fs90}I am now down to one turbo charger,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.04,0:54:46.48,字幕,,0,0,0,,但我又回到了比赛里\N{\fs90}but I'm back in the race.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.35,0:54:56.15,字幕,,0,0,0,,是的 我在开一台雷诺DCI 120拖车\N{\fs90}Yes, I'm at the wheel of a Renault DCI 120 tow truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.22,0:54:57.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,更重要的是 我决定\N{\fs90}And what's more, I've decided
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.79,0:55:00.49,字幕,,0,0,0,,飞奔至港口 \N{\fs90}to head for the port as the crow flies.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.63,0:55:05.63,字幕,,0,0,0,,太棒了\N{\fs90}Oh, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.10,0:55:12.37,字幕,,0,0,0,,噢天啊 不\N{\fs90}Oh, God, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.51,0:55:16.71,字幕,,0,0,0,,这边好像对了\N{\fs90}This looks good.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.38,0:55:20.04,字幕,,0,0,0,,没错 渡轮码头\N{\fs90}Yes. Ferry terminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.18,0:55:22.58,字幕,,0,0,0,,这就对了\N{\fs90}This is all correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.19,0:55:28.39,字幕,,0,0,0,,那是杰里米\N{\fs90}That is Jeremy!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.42,0:55:29.45,字幕,,0,0,0,,那是哈蒙德\N{\fs90}There's Hammond!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.52,0:55:31.19,字幕,,0,0,0,,他在干什么\N{\fs90}What is he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.26,0:55:33.43,字幕,,0,0,0,,干掉他\N{\fs90}Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.39,0:55:37.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,我必须要赢\N{\fs90}I have to win. I have to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.90,0:55:41.97,字幕,,0,0,0,,有个环岛 哦 天啊 真的么\N{\fs90}A roundabout. Oh, bloody hell. Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.80,0:55:49.21,字幕,,0,0,0,,问题是 勒阿弗尔的码头太大了\N{\fs90}The problem was that the port of Le Havre is so vast
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.27,0:55:52.71,字幕,,0,0,0,,又复杂 很容易迷路\N{\fs90}and so complex, it was very easy to get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.78,0:55:55.88,字幕,,0,0,0,,谁都有可能赢\N{\fs90}This was still anyone's race.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.69,0:56:02.49,字幕,,0,0,0,,哈蒙德在哪里 梅在哪里\N{\fs90}Where is Hammond? Where is May?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.55,0:56:04.17,字幕,,0,0,0,,船在哪里\N{\fs90}Where is the boat?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.56,0:56:07.73,字幕,,0,0,0,,加油啊\N{\fs90}Come on, come on, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.90,0:56:21.14,字幕,,0,0,0,,这条路不对 这条路不对\N{\fs90}This is wrong. This is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.75,0:56:30.08,字幕,,0,0,0,,应该是沿着这条路走\N{\fs90}It's got to be down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.15,0:56:32.08,字幕,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs90}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.75,0:56:38.59,字幕,,0,0,0,,刚才油门被地毯卡住了吗\N{\fs90}Did I have some carpet stuck under the throttle?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.66,0:56:41.96,字幕,,0,0,0,,我的DCI 120简直快得飞起啊\N{\fs90}Cos my DCI 120's going like a bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.97,0:56:53.08,字幕,,0,0,0,,啊 没错 就是这里\N{\fs90}Yes! This looks good. This is the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.58,0:56:59.71,字幕,,0,0,0,,好货车 乖货车 船就在那里\N{\fs90}Good van. Good van. The boat is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.78,0:57:03.01,字幕,,0,0,0,,哈蒙德已经到了 梅到了吗\N{\fs90}There is Richard Hammond. Is James May here?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.48,0:57:06.08,字幕,,0,0,0,,不 他没到\N{\fs90}No, he is not!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.15,0:57:07.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,他没到\N{\fs90}He is not.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.79,0:57:09.69,字幕,,0,0,0,,好棒\N{\fs90}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.66,0:57:14.19,字幕,,0,0,0,,哈哈 看到梅了吗\N{\fs90}Ha-ha! No May?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.66,0:57:20.23,字幕,,0,0,0,,不 他们不可能看见我\N{\fs90}No, and there wouldn't be,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.30,0:57:22.50,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为我在港口的另一边\N{\fs90}because I was in another part of the port
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.57,0:57:24.57,字幕,,0,0,0,,我有自己的计划\N{\fs90}with my own travel plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.64,0:57:26.94,字幕,,0,0,0,,昨晚 在他们两个上床之后\N{\fs90}Last night, after the other two had gone to bed,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.01,0:57:29.51,字幕,,0,0,0,,我预定了一艘我们公司的游艇\N{\fs90}I arranged for our company yacht
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.54,0:57:32.61,字幕,,0,0,0,,让它在码头等我\N{\fs90}to be waiting for me in the harbour.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.68,0:57:34.68,字幕,,0,0,0,,看 它在那儿\N{\fs90}And there it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.52,0:57:43.82,字幕,,0,0,0,,我只要开过去 跳上船\N{\fs90}I simply drive up, hop aboard,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.89,0:57:45.56,字幕,,0,0,0,,然后就可以上路了\N{\fs90}and then we'll be on our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.12,0:58:14.99,字幕,,0,0,0,,-很遗憾 他活了下来 -等一下\N{\fs90}- He lived, annoyingly. - Hold on, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.05,0:58:16.86,字幕,,0,0,0,,等一下 哈蒙德\N{\fs90}Hold on. Hammond.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.92,0:58:18.69,字幕,,0,0,0,,你得解释下这个\N{\fs90}I need to ask you about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.76,0:58:22.26,字幕,,0,0,0,,为什么你要在我的车上贴一个"Déshabille"\N{\fs90}Why did you stick "Déshabille"on my car?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.33,0:58:25.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为你当时残疾了啊\N{\fs90}Because you were disabled.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.06,0:58:29.57,字幕,,0,0,0,,Déshabille的意思是一丝不挂 你个蠢货\N{\fs90}Déshabille means undressed, you moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.57,0:58:31.37,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们就不要纠结于\N{\fs90}Let's not get bogged down
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.44,0:58:32.90,字幕,,0,0,0,,噢我不会说法语 之类的话了\N{\fs90}with "Ooh, can't speak French."
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.97,0:58:36.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,言归正传 詹姆斯梅\N{\fs90}Let's get to the point which is, James May,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.81,0:58:39.91,字幕,,0,0,0,,你输了 还把公司的游艇撞坏了\N{\fs90}you lost and you broke the company yacht.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.98,0:58:41.68,字幕,,0,0,0,,-是的 -等等\N{\fs90}- You did. - Hang on a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.75,0:58:44.68,字幕,,0,0,0,,我的车比你们的离英国更近\N{\fs90}My car got closer to England than yours did.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.75,0:58:46.45,字幕,,0,0,0,,没错 但是我觉得\N{\fs90}Yes, but the other thing it got closest to
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.59,0:58:48.15,字幕,,0,0,0,,它离海底更近吧\N{\fs90}was the bottom of the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.22,0:58:49.85,字幕,,0,0,0,,你们说那些都没用\N{\fs90}All of that is irrelevant
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.92,0:58:51.59,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为我的车才是最好的\N{\fs90}because my car was the best,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.66,0:58:53.42,字幕,,0,0,0,,整段旅程它都没坏\N{\fs90}cos it didn't go wrong at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.49,0:58:55.51,字幕,,0,0,0,,我的车也极为可靠\N{\fs90}Mine was perfectly reliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.60,0:58:58.71,字幕,,0,0,0,,嗯 我的车就像詹姆斯的胳膊一样靠谱\N{\fs90}Mm-hm. Mine was as reliable as James's arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.88,0:59:02.27,字幕,,0,0,0,,最离奇的是 没人能弄清楚\N{\fs90}And the extraordinary thing is, no-one can work out
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.33,0:59:03.64,字幕,,0,0,0,,那辆车到底哪里有问题\N{\fs90}what was wrong with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.70,0:59:05.90,字幕,,0,0,0,,它从拖车上掉下去了\N{\fs90}It fell off the back of a lorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.97,0:59:07.87,字幕,,0,0,0,,不 没人能搞清楚它到底哪儿坏了\N{\fs90}No- one can work out what fault it had
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.94,0:59:10.71,字幕,,0,0,0,,以至于要上拖车\N{\fs90}that caused it to be on the lorry in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.78,0:59:13.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,现在这段都拍完了9个月了\N{\fs90}And even nine months down the line,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.54,0:59:17.31,字幕,,0,0,0,,两位专业的玛莎拉蒂技师被彻底难住了\N{\fs90}two trained Maserati mechanics are totally stumped.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.40,0:59:19.35,字幕,,0,0,0,,这真是个令人难以理解问题\N{\fs90}It is an unfathomable fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.42,0:59:21.22,字幕,,0,0,0,,是啊 所以从法国北部的测试\N{\fs90}Yeah, so what we can conclude
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.29,0:59:24.49,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们得出如下结论\N{\fs90}from our exhaustive testing in the north of France
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.62,0:59:26.63,字幕,,0,0,0,,如果你买了一台二手玛莎拉蒂\N{\fs90}is that if you buy a used Maserati,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.69,0:59:29.99,字幕,,0,0,0,,有66%的概率能碰到台正常运转的\N{\fs90}you have a 66% chance of it working.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.36,0:59:32.63,字幕,,0,0,0,,听起来还不错嘛\N{\fs90}They're not bad odds.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.63,0:59:33.90,字幕,,0,0,0,,你要是在做眼科手术前\N{\fs90}You wouldn't say that
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.97,0:59:36.27,字幕,,0,0,0,,听到这个成功率 你肯定不会这么说\N{\fs90}if you were having an eye operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.33,0:59:38.77,字幕,,0,0,0,,是啊 随着这个失望的消息 节目也该结束了\N{\fs90}Exactly. And on that terrible disappointment, it's time to end.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.84,0:59:41.37,字幕,,0,0,0,,感谢各位的收看 晚安\N{\fs90}Thank you so much for watching. Good night!
